# Loading Packages 
```{r}
packages = c('sp', 'rgdal', 'rgeos', 'sf', 'tidyverse')
for (p in packages){
  if(!require(p, character.only = T)){
    install.packages(p)
  }
  library(p,character.only = T)
}
```
